{"tid":2047472,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"東亞：(屌 有鬼嘅) 未就出售中港銀行業務與外界討論","createTime":"2020-06-02T06:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T11:26:23.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9d577012a001886d8bbd1872101a91aa16481a52","tid":2047472,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"東亞：未就出售中港銀行業務與外界討論<br />\n02.06.2020 12:56<br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》報道，東亞銀行(<a href=\"http://00023.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00023.HK&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=9f6e71bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00023.HK</a>)初步討論出售香港及中國內地銀行業務，東亞其後澄清，正進行全面策略檢討，當中並未就出售香港或中國內地銀行業務與外界討論，亦未就本行業務和資產的策略選項作任何決定。<br />\n<br />\n東亞說，一直與顧問高盛緊密合作，繼續全面評估業務和資產，並專注識別潛在策略交易，交易將可提升現有業務和資產的價值，以及潛在非核心資產的策略選項，將在九月底或之前公布檢討的最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1297420&amp;csid=261_368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1297420%26csid%3D261_368&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=d33b970b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1297420&amp;csid=261_368</a>"},{"pid":"b8749585a332aa26d1016f79793fcff1479dbe1b","tid":2047472,"uid":252993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"唔跌返落去，即係市場唔信呢個澄清"},{"pid":"7377b541be91d2abc7c1ed180da509648445317c","tid":2047472,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"邊有人會買，蝕死你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f36b6189997b704f26ae01914f888a0b58ea69","tid":2047472,"uid":57543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"撤資<img 